            "content_html" : "\u003cp\u003eDimitri Fontaine, a PostgreSQL Major Contributor, posted \u003ca\n  class=\"gblog-markdown__link\"\n  href=\"https://theartofpostgresql.com/blog/2019-09-why-postgres/\"\n  \n\u003eWhy Postgres?\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eCrunchy Data posted \u003ca\n  class=\"gblog-markdown__link\"\n  href=\"https://www.crunchydata.com/why-postgres\"\n  \n\u003eWhy Postgres?\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e2ndQuadrant\u0026rsquo;s Kirk Roybal posted \u003ca\n  class=\"gblog-markdown__link\"\n  href=\"https://www.2ndquadrant.com/en/blog/postgresql-is-the-worlds-best-database/\"\n  \n\u003ePostgreSQL is the worlds’ best database\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e2ndQuadrant\u0026rsquo;s Simon Riggs posted \u003ca\n  class=\"gblog-markdown__link\"\n  href=\"https://www.enterprisedb.com/blog/4-reasons-postgresql-was-named-database-management-system-year-2020\"\n  \n\u003e4 Reasons PostgreSQL was Named Database Management System of the Year 2020\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eEDB\u0026rsquo;s Bruce Momjian posted \u003ca\n  class=\"gblog-markdown__link\"\n  href=\"https://momjian.us/main/blogs/pgblog/2020.html#September_16_2020\"\n  \n\u003eWhy Not to Choose Postgres\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eEDB\u0026rsquo;s Bruce Momjian posted \u003ca\n  class=\"gblog-markdown__link\"\n  href=\"https://momjian.us/main/blogs/pgblog/2020.html#July_8_2020\"\n  \n\u003ePostgres Marketing\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n"
